  <prompt>Edit `src/client/shared/Spaarke.DailyBriefing.Components/src/services/notificationService.ts` to include a `$filter` clause `createdon ge &lt;now - window&gt;` in `fetchNotifications`. Map the user setting (12h/24h/48h/7d) to ISO date computation. Watch for R3 PR #451 overlap on the same file — coordinate via notes/risks.md.</prompt>
  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Follow ADRs strictly. Expert in Fluent UI v9 + React hooks + Xrm.WebApi.</role>
  <goal>`fetchNotifications` query string includes `$filter=createdon ge {iso}` where ISO timestamp = now minus configured window. Setting value drives the boundary. Default falls back to 24h if preference missing.</goal>
