  <steps>
    <step order="1">Open `notificationService.ts`; locate `fetchNotifications` and identify current `$filter`/query construction</step>
    <step order="2">Add a helper `computeTimeWindowIso(setting: TimeWindowSetting): string` mapping 12h/24h/48h/7d to ISO timestamps (now - delta)</step>
    <step order="3">Append `createdon ge &lt;iso&gt;` to the `$filter` clause (compose with existing AND clauses correctly)</step>
    <step order="4">Read `timeWindow` from passed-in preferences; default to 24h if missing/invalid</step>
    <step order="5">Update or add Jest unit test confirming `$filter` contains correct ISO for each of the 4 setting values</step>
